{"id": 2735, "genre": 1000, "title": "看电影/阅读时，你能接受哪些“划重点”的习惯？", "description": "一种跟“小时候爱在课本上划杠”十分相似的肌肉记忆。（题图来自：iStock ©️ Anna_Isaeva）", "record_count": 5714, "comment_count": 13, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190114205230qH1trCpA2QkRJ7gi.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-01-20T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 5225, "title": "看电影/阅读时，你能接受哪些“划重点”的习惯？", "content": "日常中你都看到过/经历过哪些“划重点”后遗症？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 322707, "content": "一篇文章在手机上划太多次，就会归入“太长不看”", "image": "img/option/option/20190114204312lbJYRMZg7TpVnxh2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 322710, "content": "先去转发/评论区看脱水版，再倒回来看原文", "image": "img/option/option/20190114204340dSVchv6m1lDGH7bP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 322712, "content": "先收藏然后跳着读，主要记几个关键词", "image": "img/option/option/20190114204159PA9kqdEcLW46KrDh.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 322714, "content": "一条微博如果超过 140 个字符，就只看前几行", "image": "img/option/option/20190114204138sSa9WRitXJ2PnjD3.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 322715, "content": "读完全文如果没找到结论，会觉得自己“白看了”", "image": "img/option/option/201901142039591iQuofr7eAK4yBI0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 322723, "content": "习惯用“划重点”“敲黑板”一键定位重点段落", "image": "img/option/option/20190114203907v9Wi8fYZyAj2eqmR.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 322728, "content": "注意力偶尔会被文中出现的表情包带偏", "image": "img/option/option/201901142038573Ut40JcaSRCDkn7p.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 322741, "content": "看书时，最好先配点解读以免“看不懂”", "image": "img/option/option/20190114203845QJSufZzAxLDyg83d.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 322742, "content": "在B站看恐怖片，先确定高能情节在几分几秒", "image": "img/option/option/20190114203735VO0fFbLxavoH8ZDj.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 322743, "content": "看电影之前，先搜搜里头有多少彩蛋", "image": "img/option/option/201901142035478joIG1rzlL6aOBs9.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}